info.author: dot_j
info.description: Mumbles is a plugin-driven, DBus based notification system written for the Gnome desktop. Similar to libnotify notifications and Growl for OSX (http://growl.info), Mumbles aims to provide a modern notification system for the GNU/Linux Desktop.
info.name: mumbles
info.summary: Mumbles is notification system for the Gnome desktop.
